{"tid":1553731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武走得太前，做人要有公關！文宣多一個就好多！","createTime":"2019-09-08T16:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T08:04:55.000Z","uid":9049,"like":57,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"4867488cf2cc9ccdee5b39b314474722ad088be8","tid":1553731,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:47:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">做人要有公關！</span></span>文宣多一個就好多！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">重建連儂牆</span></span>要人！連儂牆係我地嘅廣告版；現時後勤補給乏力！<br />\n依家政府政黨出盡奶力<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">搶民意</span></span>；欺騙市民；<br />\n最近新聞淨係播勇武搞破壞；<br />\n等民意逆轉就變真暴徒啦！<br />\n唔好以為唔會逆轉，5年前失敗經驗呢？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">梁天琦封信</span></span>又唔記得左啦？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>唔係屌你地搞地鐵，而係有手足行得比較慢<br />\n要d時間適應，等埋後面爬緊山上緊黎嘅手足好冇？</strong><br />\n<br />\n其實打左咁多字，我想問：<br />\n<ins><strong>每次有人被捕，個心就好唔舒服<br />\n有冇方法可以減輕一下？</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTemplate:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>衛城長久戰，生活中抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全之下，免費港鐵；二人同遊，一人免費<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！連繫左鄰右里<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2Bmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=a9cdff01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 低消費，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.09"},{"pid":"b5f6690c8265c7abbdb78b0cce34be1c8cf790be","tid":1553731,"uid":164517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f7b96edd38b09e2d40db9416b03da3ae369eb0","tid":1553731,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:52:40.000Z","msg":"最近文宣有困難，要組隊參與<br />\n<br />\n又要擔驚受怕，求大家幫手"},{"pid":"d524bb7578c75db4087984e454be17ae8eb58d5e","tid":1553731,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:01:05.000Z","msg":"Push 1/10"},{"pid":"3782b85f9f4705c7d45e9eecc78a6b2cb7a56d27","tid":1553731,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:02:51.000Z","msg":"Push 2/10"},{"pid":"69474fd92fbec2b67990a4f334c3dbe92810e4fc","tid":1553731,"uid":44181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:04:13.000Z","msg":"公關同文宣交返比和理非！"},{"pid":"ecb1bb3455b324dbdc411f50556deef9511f0edf","tid":1553731,"uid":153476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:04:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475973922e1ff59a90cd7dcae707510252b7312a","tid":1553731,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:04:48.000Z","msg":"Push 3/10"},{"pid":"d76569b37ab0fac1a35d4b380af6e784be73742b","tid":1553731,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:06:12.000Z","msg":"Push 4/10"},{"pid":"deb538d626f560c76acbb98d1378c0cfe8c14248","tid":1553731,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"