id":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:30:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人欠勇武派實在太多, 邊個屌勇武邊個就係鬼</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf99dde6b468e29729a15fa85bc19055cbddfe3f","tid":1553731,"uid":235111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:56:53.000Z","msg":"Puah"},{"pid":"c30ecf05fdf2c25fb3cf402230186eab30a3672d","tid":1553731,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:01:15.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n建議呢個星期全力重建連儂牆<br />\n913 914 915 活動要去，但完左請起返連儂牆<br />\n而唔係衝擊或散水或轉場<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">等所有人知道發生緊咩事先！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">連儂牆起源於反共，呢條戰線不能倒！</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n勇武走得太前，後勤補給不足，文宣唔夠人！<br />\n做人要有公關！文宣多一個就好多！連儂牆要人！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>衛城長久戰，生活中抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">抵制</span>「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全之下，<span style=\"color: red;\">免費港鐵</span>；二人同遊，一人免費<br />\n3. 夜晚<span style=\"color: red;\">十點吶喊</span>！！！連繫左鄰右里<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: red;\">每日一post</span>，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2Bmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=a9cdff01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會事務，做陪審員啦<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.09"},{"pid":"fb5f72620c7378243554447c538ab947e6424de5","tid":1553731,"uid":264996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:01:48.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（集思廣益）連儂牆唔夠文宣之建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1555513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1555513</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b4ac229b7aa05391d2feeafb56d193fbe2f344af","tid":1553731,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:03:05.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n建議呢個星期全力重建連儂牆<br />\n913 914 915 活動要去，但完左請起返連儂牆<br />\n而唔係衝擊或散水或轉場<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">等所有人知道發生緊咩事先！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">連儂牆起源於反共，呢條戰線不能倒！</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n勇武走得太前，後勤補給不足，文宣唔夠人！<br />\n做人要有公關！文宣多一個就好多！連儂牆要人！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>衛城長久戰，生活中抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">抵制</span>「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全之下，<span style=\"color: red;\">免費港鐵</span>；二人同遊，一人免費<br />\n3. 夜晚<span style=\"color: red;\">十點吶喊</span>！！！連繫左鄰右里<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: red;\">每日一post</span>，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2Bmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=a9cdff01\" data-auto-link tar